title: WIZ811MJ
description:
WIZnet W5100 Network Module with MagJack - WIZ811MJ

WIZnet's WIZ811MJ is a breakout board for the W5100 embedded TCP/IP chip. Also included on the board is a RJ-45 MagJack Connector (RJ45 with X'FMR).

See http://www.sparkfun.com/commerce/product_info.php?products_id=9473 for more documentation and info.
